snippet.title: World Association of Girl Guides and Girl Scouts
snippet.description: The World Association of Girl Guides and Girl Scouts is the largest voluntary Movement dedicated to girls and young women in the world representing ten million girls and  women from 152 countries. This is our YouTube channel where you can hear directly from the women of girls of our diverse Movement.
